comments.body: @jpstroop There is already a "Participation" field with "Presenter" as one of the options. Would it be OK to tag the requests with a "Presenter" label if that level of participation has been selected?

The approval screen already does show the participation field which will display "presenter" when that has been selected. I'm not sure adding another tag makes much sense on that screen. We could add this filed as displayed and filterable value on the various reporting screens. How does that sound?
Oh, interesting. I wonder if certain departments just aren't using it. I think we can just close this--looking at the UI, I think what is there is adequate.
